fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 gained 59.75 points or 0.32% to settle at 18,593.85. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, added 0.11% to 11.14. RIL, Tata Chemicals and ICICI Bank were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The June 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 29 June 2023.
